No.55/4/CF-64 (1)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
IMMEDIATE
New Delhi, the 15th June 1964.
The undersigned is directed to state that the Minister of
State and the Deputy Ministers named in the enclosed list assumed
office with effect from the forenoon of Monday June 15, 1964.
(D.P. Chopra)
for Cabinet Secretary.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy with a copy of the enclosure forwarded to
the Principal Private Secretary to the Prime Minister/the
Private Secretary to the Prime Minister, for information,
Copy with a copy of the enclosure forwarded to the
Secretary to the President/the Private Secretary to the
Vico-President, for information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.

Copy with a copy of the enclosure forwarded to all
Secretaries/Special Secretaries/Additional Secretaries to the
Government of India/Chairman, Railwey Board/Seeretary,
Election Commission, for information.
Gopy with a copy of the enclosure forwarded to all
Ministries of the Government of India/Department of Parliamentary
Affairs/Planning Commission/Depar tment of Atomic Energy/
Prime Ministor's Secretariat/Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha
Secretariat, for information.
(D.P, Chopra )
Under Secretary to the Cabinet,
"MANOCHA"
